                        br
                        | innovation has no limit
                        br
                        | with BAP
                    p Born with an inspiring vision “Contribute innovation to the world”, BAP IT CO.,JSC. stands for Be Advanced Partner, lives to treasure our Client and Staff as our lifetime-partner, continuously innovate and grow together.
